; Regression test for issue #786:
; Transaction check doesn't give line number for included file.
; When a "check" directive fails, the warning should report both the
; location of the triggering transaction and the account directive
; where the check expression is defined.

include 786.dat

test bal
          -10.00 EUR  bar
           10.00 EUR  foo
--------------------
                   0
__ERROR__
Warning: "$sourcepath/test/regress/786.dat", line 4: Transaction check failed: has_tag("test")
  (check expression at "$sourcepath/test/regress/786.dat", line 1)
end test
